TEXT 64 1040 Left 1 !.meas TRAN turn_on_sensor FIND V(sense) WHEN V(fan_en)=2.5 RISE=1
TEXT 64 1072 Left 1 !.meas TRAN turn_off_sensor FIND V(sense) WHEN V(fan_en)=2.5 FALL=1
